headline: Beyond AI: Should You Buy This Top Stock That's Up 232% in the Past 5 Years?
summary: Investors continue to be enamored with AI stocks like Nvidia, shares of which have soared in recent years.  Boring companies like Costco can still be big winners thanks to competitive strengths and customer loyalty.  Unless you've been sleeping under a rock for the past three years, you're fully aware of just how much artificial intelligence (AI) has taken over the narratives in the stock market and the broader economy.
